#----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------#
#                                     DESCRIPTION
#----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------#
#  cds :
# cds, when issued from the command prompt in Terminal, iTerm, or xterm,  will cd 
# into the directory corresponding to the web page displayed in Safari.

#----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------#
#                                        TODO
#----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------#


#----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------#
